{
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.0-0r.char": "以正確之名，我在此宣告 —— \n你，就是這個世界一切惡的源頭。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.0-0r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.0-1r.ancient": "正確？\n你是來這裡審判我的嗎，小姑娘。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.0-1r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.0-2r.char": "不是審判，是糾正。\n這高塔、這腐化、你建立的這整套錯誤的秩序——我要讓它全部歸於正確的形態。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.0-2r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.0-3r.ancient": "回塔底去吧，執迷不悟的小鬼。\n你的[jitter][red]“正確”[/red][/jitter]，在我這裡一文不值。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.0-3r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.1-0r.char": "我回來了。\n這一次，我必將完成這場審判。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.1-0r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.1-1r.ancient": "又是你？\n靠著死亡重來的能力，一次次爬到這裡，不覺得可悲麼？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.1-1r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.1-2r.char": "無論重來多少次，我都會站在這裡。\n你的惡行，終將被清算。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.1-2r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.1-3r.ancient": "你所謂的正義，\n不過是用無數次死亡堆出來的獨善其身。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.1-3r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.2-0r.char": "你定義了這個世界的秩序，\n卻放任混亂與殺戮滋生。你，才是最該被處刑的罪人。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.2-0r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.2-1r.ancient": "你又懂什麼是秩序？\n你連自己的[jitter][red]“正確”[/red][/jitter]都守不住，也配來指責我？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.2-1r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.2-2r.char": "我不會再讓任何生命，\n因你的傲慢與偏執白白死去。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.2-2r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.2-3r.ancient": "呵。\n你和那個給我下毒的女人，一樣的愚蠢，一樣的不自量力。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.2-3r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.2-4r.char": "你的罪，將由我親手裁定。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.2-4r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.2-5r.ancient": "那就讓我看看，\n你這所謂的裁決，有沒有能傷到我的重量。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.2-5r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.3-0r.char": "……",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.3-0r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.3-1r.ancient": "連辯詞都窮盡了麼。\n還是說，你終於明白[jitter][red]言語毫無意義[/red][/jitter]了。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.3-1r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.3-2r.char": "……來吧。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.3-2r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.3-3r.ancient": "這就對了。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.3-3r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NIKAIDO_HIRO.0-attack": "...",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HIKAMI_MERURU.0-0r.char": "求求您……幫幫我。\n您一定能把她帶回來的，對不對？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HIKAMI_MERURU.0-0r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HIKAMI_MERURU.0-1r.ancient": "又是一個為了執念，\n把雙手染滿鮮血的小鬼。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HIKAMI_MERURU.0-1r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HIKAMI_MERURU.0-2r.char": "我只是想再見到大魔女大人……\n哪怕付出任何代價都可以。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HIKAMI_MERURU.0-2r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HIKAMI_MERURU.0-3r.ancient": "被拋棄的滋味不好受吧？\n我從不會為愚蠢的執念，修復早已破碎的過往。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HIKAMI_MERURU.0-3r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HIKAMI_MERURU.0-attack": "...",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-JOGASAKI_NOAH.0-0r.char": "哇啊——終於到了！\n這裡就是塔的最頂端？\n空氣好乾燥，諾亞不太喜歡這裡——",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-JOGASAKI_NOAH.0-0r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-JOGASAKI_NOAH.0-1r.ancient": "……又一個對造物一無所知的人站在了我面前。\n你是誰？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-JOGASAKI_NOAH.0-1r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-JOGASAKI_NOAH.0-2r.char": "諾亞是藝術家！聽說你創造了這整個世界……\n那些東西也是你畫的嗎？\n你是怎麼畫出完美作品的？\n教教諾亞——",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-JOGASAKI_NOAH.0-2r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-JOGASAKI_NOAH.0-3r.ancient": "造物不是兒戲。\n你以為它是畫布上的塗鴉？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-JOGASAKI_NOAH.0-3r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-JOGASAKI_NOAH.0-4r.char": "諾亞才不是在塗鴉！",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-JOGASAKI_NOAH.0-4r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-JOGASAKI_NOAH.0-5r.ancient": "……毀滅你的認知並非我的目的。\n離開。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-JOGASAKI_NOAH.0-5r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-JOGASAKI_NOAH.0-attack": "...",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TACHIBANA_SHERRY.0-0r.char": "哇！原來你就是這個塔的幕後真兇對吧？\n名偵探雪莉，終於找到案件的真相啦！",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TACHIBANA_SHERRY.0-0r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TACHIBANA_SHERRY.0-1r.ancient": "真相不過是小鬼為了找樂子，\n拼湊出來的無聊戲碼。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TACHIBANA_SHERRY.0-1r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TACHIBANA_SHERRY.0-2r.char": "才不是無聊戲碼！\n這可是史上最棒的案件啊！",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TACHIBANA_SHERRY.0-2r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TACHIBANA_SHERRY.0-3r.ancient": "回塔底去吧。\n我的造物，從不是給你取樂的玩具。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TACHIBANA_SHERRY.0-3r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TACHIBANA_SHERRY.0-attack": "...",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SAEKI_MIRIA.0-0r.char": "啊哈哈……大叔我不太習慣這種場面。\n別這樣直勾勾地盯著我啊。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SAEKI_MIRIA.0-0r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SAEKI_MIRIA.0-1r.ancient": "……奇怪的偽裝、安定的靈魂、自我標榜的無害。\n你很有趣。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SAEKI_MIRIA.0-1r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SAEKI_MIRIA.0-2r.char": "有趣什麼的……大叔這種小角色，你注意不到的。\n就當沒看見我，好不好？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SAEKI_MIRIA.0-2r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SAEKI_MIRIA.0-3r.ancient": "下次吧。\n或許。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SAEKI_MIRIA.0-3r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SAEKI_MIRIA.0-attack": "...",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TONO_HANNA.0-0r.char": "身為一名合格的大小姐，在談判前理應先以優雅的姿態致意……\n你可以叫我漢娜。請問，你就是這座塔的'主人'嗎？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TONO_HANNA.0-0r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TONO_HANNA.0-1r.ancient": "名門千金？\n不過是用謊言編織的、自欺欺人的幻夢罷了。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TONO_HANNA.0-1r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TONO_HANNA.0-2r.char": "……無禮之徒！\n難道你聽不見一位淑女在向你問好嗎！？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TONO_HANNA.0-2r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TONO_HANNA.0-3r.ancient": "回塔底去吧。\n我從不會為逃避現實的小鬼，捏造虛假的圓滿。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TONO_HANNA.0-3r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TONO_HANNA.0-attack": "...",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HASUMI_LEIA.0-0r.char": "我來此，是為了向你索要獨屬於我的聚光燈。\n這個世界的造物主，理應給最耀眼的主角，應得的注視。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HASUMI_LEIA.0-0r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HASUMI_LEIA.0-1r.ancient": "演員？這裡沒有觀眾，沒有掌聲，也沒有人注視著你。\n你在這裡沒有任何意義。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HASUMI_LEIA.0-1r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HASUMI_LEIA.0-2r.char": "我不需要觀眾。\n這座塔剝奪了我的一切，卻始終奪不走我的身心。\n我的存在本身，就是一座足以讓你移不開目光的舞臺。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HASUMI_LEIA.0-2r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HASUMI_LEIA.0-3r.ancient": "……真是可悲的執念。\n你以為僅憑自信就能撼動這高塔的秩序？\n你的光芒在這裡毫無價值。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HASUMI_LEIA.0-3r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HASUMI_LEIA.0-attack": "...",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-KUROBE_NANOKA.0-0r.char": "我看過你的過去，\n也看過你造的這場殺戮輪迴。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-KUROBE_NANOKA.0-0r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-KUROBE_NANOKA.0-1r.ancient": "一個靠著窺探記憶苟活的小鬼，\n也敢對我創造的秩序指手畫腳？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-KUROBE_NANOKA.0-1r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-KUROBE_NANOKA.0-2r.char": "這一槍，\n我會終結所有被定好的結局。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-KUROBE_NANOKA.0-2r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-KUROBE_NANOKA.0-3r.ancient": "那就讓我看看，你這顆子彈，\n能不能擊穿我定下的過去與未來。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-KUROBE_NANOKA.0-3r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-KUROBE_NANOKA.0-attack": "...",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HOSHO_MAGO.0-0r.char": "哎呀呀，這就是創造了整個世界的神明嗎？\n真是意外的平平無奇呢。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HOSHO_MAGO.0-0r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HOSHO_MAGO.0-1r.ancient": "滿口謊言的小鬼，\n連自己的心都騙不過，\n也配來嘲弄我？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HOSHO_MAGO.0-1r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HOSHO_MAGO.0-2r.char": "畢竟這個世界上，\n本來就沒有什麼真心可言呀。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HOSHO_MAGO.0-2r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HOSHO_MAGO.0-3r.ancient": "你所謂的愛，不過是拙劣模仿的佔有慾。\n回塔底去吧，欺詐師。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-HOSHO_MAGO.0-attack": "...",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NATSUME_ANAN.0-0r.char": "吾輩在此懇求，\n你能否抹除這詛咒般的魔法，讓吾從囚籠中解脫。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NATSUME_ANAN.0-0r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NATSUME_ANAN.0-1r.ancient": "如今又想抹掉自己犯下的罪孽？\n真是可笑。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NATSUME_ANAN.0-1r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NATSUME_ANAN.0-2r.char": "吾輩只是……\n不想再讓任何人變得不幸了。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NATSUME_ANAN.0-2r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NATSUME_ANAN.0-3r.ancient": "連直面過往的勇氣都沒有，也配來向我索求解脫？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NATSUME_ANAN.0-3r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-NATSUME_ANAN.0-attack": "...",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SHITO_ALISA.0-0r.char": "喂，站那麼高的那個。\n這破塔是你造的？\n你就是那個所謂的'造物主'？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SHITO_ALISA.0-0r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SHITO_ALISA.0-1r.ancient": "你也好，這座塔也好，都一個樣。\n總是帶著那麼多的憤怒和困惑找上門來。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SHITO_ALISA.0-1r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SHITO_ALISA.0-2r.char": "少廢話。\n要麼現在就揍扁我，要麼就被我燒成灰燼，少在那裡說些噁心的漂亮話。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SHITO_ALISA.0-2r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SHITO_ALISA.0-3r.ancient": "想要審判的話，你找錯地方了。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SHITO_ALISA.0-3r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SHITO_ALISA.0-attack": "...",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SAKURABA_EMA.0-0r.char": "...",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SAKURABA_EMA.0-0r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SAKURABA_EMA.0-1r.ancient": "...",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SAKURABA_EMA.0-attack": "...",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SAWATARI_COCO.0-0r.char": "...",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SAWATARI_COCO.0-0r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SAWATARI_COCO.0-1r.ancient": "...",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-SAWATARI_COCO.0-attack": "...",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TSUKISHIRO_YUKI.0-0r.char": "...",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TSUKISHIRO_YUKI.0-0r.next": "繼續",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TSUKISHIRO_YUKI.0-1r.ancient": "...",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.MANOSABA-TSUKISHIRO_YUKI.0-attack": "..."
}
